e entertainment. Switch to the new package and get an even higher upgrade to the next package. For more information on how to reconnect or switch to the new packages, visit www.gotvafrica.com. Also, download MyGOtv app from the iOS and Android store for self-service options. #GOtvDeyYourSide <img class="alignnone wp-image-1388808 size-full" src="https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?resize=640%2C686&#038;ssl=1" alt="GOtv Discount" width="640" height="686" srcset="https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?resize=280%2C300&amp;ssl=1 280w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?resize=955%2C1024&amp;ssl=1 955w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?resize=768%2C823&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?resize=54%2C58&amp;ssl=1 54w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?resize=181%2C194&amp;ssl=1 181w, https://i2.wp.com/www.vanguardngr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Gotv2.jpg?resize=121%2C130&amp;ssl=1 121w" sizes="(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px" data-recalc-dims="1" /> Africa’s leading video entertainment company, MultiChoice, has unveiled five new packages for its DStv and GOtv platforms to deliver more quality content at great value for customers during the upcoming festive season and beyond. November 24, 2019 In "Entertainment" To lessen the impact of the ongoing socio-economic crisis, MultiChoice has announced that it will be rewarding DStv and GOtv subscribers, who are fully paid up on their subscriptions, with an upgrade to the next higher package at no extra cost. This offer will commence on Monday. Martin Mabutho, Chief… April 20, 2020 In "Entertainment" Africa’s leading video entertainment company, MultiChoice,  has unveiled five new